Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是報告書和業務議員長資料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些資料發送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局裡的情況怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封口令已經傳達下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有向一般職員公佈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,業務和往常一樣 不存在問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 加強對幹部的監視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決掉組織這些瑣事之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須消除這些多餘的雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一代姐妹的消除 進展如阿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 無聊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣代表的職務了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是最新一代最強的NEO-GIN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古水那件事 就當作是爆炸事故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 那辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 終於解除了多餘的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以進行完美的研究了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是 很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的組織 對我沒有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那獲得一切的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這隻手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力雖然可以認同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她果然很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要稍有閃失 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和銅局長 什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和我扯著一套!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到我送去的資料麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的UltimateBlade被人輕鬆幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒聽說WitchBlade有那樣的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那個女人還跟著鷹山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就總有一天會來找我的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在聽麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個一定會成為我們的殺手鑭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺手鑭?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去捕獲她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 僅靠UltimateBlade是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要借用一下導示的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那力量是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下一些後遺症 也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢 我還精神的很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們今後要避免戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你因為受傷而縮短了壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那剩下梨穗子的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你已經有做一個父親的決心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 那就請你試著當梨穗子的父親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於她來說 全世界只有你一個爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 雅音老師有一個好建議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 明天我和鷹山加梨穗子三人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你和鷹山先生和好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也一起去 這樣好麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我一起去 不就妨礙到媽媽和鷹山先生了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你在說什麼啊 梨穗子你這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小人精
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 看來該沉默的時候就要沉默啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想當梨穗子的爸爸候補呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然傷心 但為了她們兩人的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫我只能退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還有比你更痛苦的男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我是生活在陰影下的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝一杯吧 斗澤小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們同樣是被甩的人 就一起喝到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早說過我不是你想的那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在雖然還很遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不久後就會得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預感這樣告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你一個人? 你媽媽呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽突然有工作 讓我先來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是媽媽給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你和梨穗子兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造最棒的約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還說什麼別的了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說如果是鷹山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有很棒的約會計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何呢? 鷹山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選好了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 他好像生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像還剩了一些 不合口味麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…媽媽不在 您覺得很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你一直擺出一副很嚇人的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我不知道怎麼和小孩子相處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 這就簡單多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呵呵的笑就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉? 呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那樣就成了怪叔叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次 呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就讓兩人獨處果然有些草率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微在這裡等我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在跟著我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很擔心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都應該這麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事就是越早面對越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YA HOO 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 工作結束了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你啊 梨穗子
