Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你弄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一定要釣到哦 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽可不會輸給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上鉤了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 又跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 也幫我弄一下魚餌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該更豪爽的翻過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 不可以欺負鷹山先生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽從一開始就胡亂翻來翻去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子到底幫誰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽好傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 鷹山先生請用
