Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 味道不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
