Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 賣金魚的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條小的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條胖胖的也好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女兒度過一天的感想如何?
